headline: Stock Market Awaits Key Nuclear Earnings Report As Trump Continues To Bolster Industry
summary: BWX Technologies, the U.S. Navy's main nuclear reactor supplier, reports third-quarter earnings and revenue after Monday's stock market and an analyst just advised investors to build up exposure to the nuclear play.
